0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"SEO-friendly website builders\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"Website builders\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"https://aioseo.com/?p=64570\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:457:\"<p>Looking for the best website builder for SEO? Then you&#8217;ve come to the right place. Search engine optimization (SEO) plays a massive role in the success of any business. That&#8217;s why, when building your website, you need to employ a&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-website-builder-for-seo/\">Best Website Builder for SEO In 2022: 12 Amazing Builders to Check Out</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Kato Nkhoma\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29370:\"<p>Looking for the best website builder for SEO?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Then you&#8217;ve come to the right place.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Search engine optimization (SEO) plays a massive role in the success of any business. That&#8217;s why, when building your website, you need to employ a website builder designed with SEO in mind.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>What is a Website Builder?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A website builder is a software, program or tool designed to help you create professional-looking websites without the need for any coding knowledge. You don&#8217;t need to hire a designer or developer with a website builder. Instead, all you have to do is choose a template and customize yours according to your taste.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To make it easy for newbies, most website builders feature drag-and-drop functionality. This means you can swap out elements of your website as you wish.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>However, not all website builders are built the same, as you&#8217;ll soon find out. That&#8217;s why you must make sure you pick the right one for your website needs, especially where SEO is concerned.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>How to Pick the Best Website Builder for SEO</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>With so many website builders out there, picking the right one can be a nightmare. To help you narrow down your search, you can use the following criteria to ensure your choice is the right one:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Ease-of-use</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>While most website builders are easy to use, they usually come with a slight learning curve, particularly if you&#8217;re new to building websites. That&#8217;s why ease-of-use must be a priority when looking for your next website builder. Finding your way around a website builder shouldn&#8217;t be a hassle. Everything should be easy, from adding basic pages to more complex features (like galleries).</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Affordable and Scalable</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Another important consideration to make as you search for a website builder for SEO is affordability. Particularly if you&#8217;re a small business, your budget is limited, requiring that you be thrifty when investing in your website.&nbsp;Besides affordability, you also need to ensure that your website builder will grow with your business as it grows. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Designed to Cater for Your Specific Needs</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Most website builders are better at building certain types of websites than others. For example, some are tailored for e-commerce stores, others for membership sites, and others for content sites.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Search Engine-Friendly</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Of course, you want your website to rank well. That&#8217;s the only way to drive organic traffic to your site. That&#8217;s why an important part of a website builder is its SEO-friendliness.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>The Best Website Builder for SEO: Our Top 12</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Now that you know what a website builder is and what to look for in one, let&#8217;s start looking for the best website builder for SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>1. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Self-hosted WordPress</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">WordPress</a> is one of the world&#8217;s most loved website builders on the planet and powers close to <a href=\"https://w3techs.com/blog/entry/40_percent_of_the_web_uses_wordpress\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">40% of the internet</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"447\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-website-builder-for-seo-wordpress-1.png\" alt=\"WordPress is probably the best website builder for SEO as it makes optimization super easy.\" class=\"wp-image-64576\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-website-builder-for-seo-wordpress-1.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-website-builder-for-seo-wordpress-1-300x192.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-website-builder-for-seo-wordpress-1-600x383.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides being one of the oldest website builders on the market, users love WordPress for being:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Easy to use</li><li>Scalable</li><li>Versatile</li><li>Affordable</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Its versatility means you can build any website you want. This is all thanks to the vast number of plugins and themes available to help you create custom websites.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Another advantage of WordPress is that it&#8217;s an open-source platform. Because of this, it offers maximum control over what you can do with your website as opposed to other website builders. For example, you can add other website builders like <a href=\"https://www.seedprod.com/\">SeedProd</a>, <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/beaver-builder/\">Beaver Builder</a>, and others to the platform to enhance flexibility.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>WordPress offers many optimization options that can help you rank better when it comes to SEO. You can also choose to use <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-seo-plugins-for-wordpress/\">SEO tools and plugins</a> like AIOSEO to help further boost your website&#8217;s SEO. For example, you can use AIOSEO to edit your canonical URLs to include your keyword. You can also edit robots.txt files and generate <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/how-to-create-an-xml-sitemap/\">XML sitemaps</a> without you having to touch a single line of code.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>One thing to note is WordPress is completely free. However, to use the platform, you&#8217;ll need to get hosting. Don&#8217;t worry. Getting hosting isn&#8217;t complicated, and it won&#8217;t cost much, especially if you use <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/bluehost/\">Bluehost</a> as your hosting provider. With Bluehost plans starting at $2.75/month, the WordPress/Bluehost deal is a bargain.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you&#8217;re looking for a website builder for SEO, WordPress ticks all the boxes (well, almost).&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>2. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/web-com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Web.com</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Looking for a DIY website builder for SEO that&#8217;s easy to use and affordable?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Then meet <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/web-com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\"