or-seo-3-easy-tips/\">add alt text to images</a>. Apart from that, the plugin library features many SEO-focused plugins designed to help you optimize all aspects of your website for SEO.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Since <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/how-to-connect-your-site-with-google-analytics/\">data and analytics</a> play a significant role in mapping out a successful SEO campaign, Weebly makes it easy to connect to Google Analytics and Search Console. Surprisingly, all these features come at a low price of $5/month for the lowest-tier plan. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3>11. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/domain-com-website-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Domain.com</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Whether you&#8217;re a hobbyist, small business owner, or a budding e-commerce store, one website builder to have on your radar is the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/domain-com-website-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Domain.com website builder</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/domain-com-website-builder/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"278\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-website-builder-for-seo-domain.png\" alt=\"Another great website builder for SEO you should consider is Domain.com.\" class=\"wp-image-64598\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-website-builder-for-seo-domain.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-website-builder-for-seo-domain-300x119.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-website-builder-for-seo-domain-600x238.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>The intuitive website builder lets you build your website with just a few clicks. All you have to do is pick one of the professional templates and use the drag-and-drop builder to create the website of your choice.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>But beautiful websites are just part of the package. Domain.com also comes with SEO features in-built to help you get your business noticed quickly. One of the most significant is the page title and meta description optimization capabilities. Add to that speed and security, and you&#8217;ve got half the SEO battle won.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For a website builder that costs $1.99/month, Domain.com is definitely a deal.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>12. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/godaddy-website-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">GoDaddy Website Builder</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>While it started as a hosting solution for small mom-and-pop businesses, GoDaddy has evolved into a complete suite of solutions that helps small businesses excel online. One of those solutions is the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/godaddy-website-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">GoDaddy Website Builder</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/godaddy-website-builder/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"345\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-website-builder-for-seo-godaddy.png\" alt=\"GoDaddy has one of the best website builders for SEO suited for small business owners.\" class=\"wp-image-64599\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-website-builder-for-seo-godaddy.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-website-builder-for-seo-godaddy-300x148.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-website-builder-for-seo-godaddy-600x296.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Even if you have no prior experience with SEO, GoDaddy&#8217;s SEO Wizard will walk you through all the tweaks you&#8217;ll need to make to optimize your website. In addition, the wizard will help you through basic <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-technical-seo-the-best-checklist-in-2022/\">technical SEO best practices</a> like optimizing your URLs to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/top-tips-for-good-on-page-seo/\">on-page SEO</a> like optimizing your content.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>GoDaddy also has a dedicated SEO team you can rope in to help if you want advanced SEO. There&#8217;s no fixed price for this service but expect to spend about $50/hour. as for the website builder itself, you can expect to pay $6.99/month.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>So, if you&#8217;d like to DIY your service but have an affordable plan B for SEO, then GoDaddy is the right website builder for you.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>The Best Website Builder for SEO — It&#8217;s Time to Build Your Website</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Building a website used to be tough. Creating one for SEO without any technical or coding experience was next to impossible. Today, thanks to advanced technology, you can choose the best website builder for SEO on this list and have your website up and running in no time.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you&#8217;re wondering which website builder we recommend, we go with WordPress. This is from over a decade of experience building websites — mainly on WordPress. We recommend WordPress because you can build virtually any type of website you want. As for SEO, you can also add powerful plugins like AIOSEO to help give your website the best chance of ranking.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>So, if you&#8217;ve chosen WordPress as your website builder of choice, go ahead and <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\">download AIOSEO today</a>.</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-website-builder-for-seo/\">Best Website Builder for SEO In 2022: 12 Amazing Builders to Check Out</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:53:\"https://aioseo.co