t\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22:\"keyword research tools\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"SEO keyword analysis\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"https://aioseo.com/?p=63844\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:442:\"<p>In search of the best SEO keyword analysis tool to help with your search marketing efforts? Keyword analysis is the process of researching the search phrases people use to search for your brand or product. It also involves analyzing the&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-seo-keyword-analysis-tool/\">8 Best SEO Keyword Analysis Tools You Need to Know in 2022</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Kato Nkhoma\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19186:\"<p>In search of the best SEO keyword analysis tool to help with your search marketing efforts?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Keyword analysis is the process of researching the search phrases people use to search for your brand or product. It also involves analyzing the search phrases your competitors use to drive visitors to their website.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>What is an SEO Keyword Analysis Tool?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>SEO keyword analysis tools are designed to help you get insights and data on keywords that will help you create content (or ads) that ranks and converts well. They present data such as:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Keyword volume</li><li>Keyword difficulty</li><li>Search metrics like clicks, cost per click, e.t.c.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Because <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-find-long-tail-keywords-and-increase-organic-traffic/\">keyword research</a> plays a huge role in successful digital marketing campaigns, SEO keyword analysis tools are integral to any marketer&#8217;s toolbox.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Why Should You Conduct Keyword Analysis?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>As mentioned above, keyword analysis plays a vital role in running successful search marketing campaigns.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>But why exactly is keyword analysis important?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A few reasons you should invest time and resources into keyword analysis include:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Drive Targeted Traffic to Your Website</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the most important reasons for conducting keyword analysis is that it helps you drive targeted traffic to your website. It&#8217;s an essential part of understanding what your customers are looking for and why they&#8217;re looking for it. Both are important as they help you focus on keywords that drive relevant and targeted traffic. And using keyword research tools will help you perform an <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-perform-website-seo-analysis-on-wordpress/\">SEO analysis</a> that will help you do just that. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Notice Search Trends</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Another reason keyword analysis is important is because it helps you notice search trends early. Being ahead of the curve and anticipating market behavior will ensure that you adjust your marketing efforts accordingly, thereby giving you an edge over your competitors.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Improve Conversion Rates</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Keyword analysis is a great way to identify search intent. Understanding search intent is a crucial step to creating content that converts well. By discovering keywords that have commercial intent, you can <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/5-reasons-why-your-website-is-not-converting/\">improve your conversion rates</a> and boost your sales.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>The Best SEO Keyword Analysis Tool — 8 Amazing Tools to Choose From</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Now that you know why keyword analysis is so important, it&#8217;s time to go shopping. It&#8217;s time to look at the eight best SEO keyword analysis tools you should have on your radar, in no particular order.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>1. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/semrush/\">Semrush</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/semrush/\">Semrush</a> is one of the world&#8217;s most popular SEO tools. One reason is that it&#8217;s an all-purpose SEO tool you can use to conduct any SEO research you want. One area in which it shines the most is keyword analysis.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Semrush&#8217;s Keyword Overview tool offers powerful ways to get a clear picture of everything you need to know about a particular keyword. For example, it gives you insight into:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Search volume</strong>: The number of people searching for the keyword.</li><li><strong>Keyword trend</strong>: Whether the keyword is growing in popularity or becoming less popular.</li><li><strong>Related keywords</strong>: These are other keywords related to yours. Using them gives search engines more context about your content.</li><li><strong>Intent</strong>. This shows the reason most searchers use your particular keyword in search. This helps you create content that meets users&#8217; search intent.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"280\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-semrush-2.png\" alt=\"Semrush is an SEO keyword analysis tool that offers a wealth of keyword data.\" class=\"wp-image-64291\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-semrush-2.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-semrush-2-300x120.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-semrush-2-600x240.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Apart from this, Semrush also shows you the keywords your competitors are ranking for. You also get to see keyword gaps you can exploit.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And if you&#8217;re working on a piece of content and want to optimize it for SEO on the fly, you&#8217;ll be glad to know that AIOSEO and Semrush work together right in your WordPress dashboard. With the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/introducing-semrush-integration/\">AIOSEO and Semrush integration</a>, you can easily find more key phrases to add to your content. And you can do that with a single click.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>How much does a robust SEO keyword analysis tool like Semrush cost?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Expect to pay $99.95/month for the base plan if you pay annually</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>2. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/ahrefs/\">Ahrefs</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/ahrefs/\">Ahrefs</a> is another SEO keyword tool you should consider adding to your tool stack.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ahrefs is similar to Semrush in many ways when it comes to its set of keyword analysis tools. The Keyword Explorer feature is an excellent tool for discovering keywords to use in your content. </p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/ahrefs/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"324\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-ahrefs-2.png\" alt=\"Ahrefs is another powerful SEO keyword analysis tool that should be on your radar.  \" class=\"wp-image-64334\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-ahrefs-2.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-ahrefs-2-300x139.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-ahrefs-2-600x278.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides discovering new keywords, Keyword Explorer also gives you insight into:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Keywords your competitors are ranking for</li><li>Keyword movement</li><li>Other keywords top-ranking pages rank for</li><li>Number of clicks on search results containing your keyword</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides being an SEO keyword analysis tool, you can use Ahrefs for many other SEO-related tasks such as <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/showcase/best-backlink-checker-tools-compared/\">backlink analysis</a>, site audits, rank tracking, and much more.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Pricing for Ahrefs starts at $99/month.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>3. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/serpstat/\">Serpstat</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>If you&#8217;re looking for a feature-rich SEO keyword analysis tool that won&#8217;t cost as much as the first two on our list, <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/serpstat/\">Serpstat</a> is it.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Serpstat is a powerful SEO tool trusted by many big brands for its versatility and ease of use. When it comes to SEO keyword analysis, you couldn&#8217;t get a better tool. For one, it makes it easy to see how you rank for your keywords, how your competitors rank, and the content that occupies SERP features. Serpstat also gives you a graphical representation of historical user interest for that keyword. This helps give you a better overview of your keyword. If you&#8217;re running PPC campaigns, it also shows you the ads that are ranking high.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/serpstat/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"512\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-keyword-analysis-tool-serpstat-2.png\" alt=\"Serpstat is another keyword analysis tool to consider thanks to being data and feature-rich.\" class=\"wp-image-64517\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-keyword-analysis-tool-serpstat-2.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-keyword-analysis-tool-serpstat-2-300x219.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-keyword-analysis-tool-serpstat-2-600x439.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>One other advantage Serpstat has is the simple and easy-to-understand dashboard. It&#8217;s so intuitive even beginners can easily find their way around.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As for pricing, Serpstat&#8217;s paid plans start at $69/month.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>4. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/mangools/\">KWFinder by Mangools</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/mangools/\">KWFinder by Mangools</a> is another SEO keyword tool that should be on your radar.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Like Semrush and Ahrefs, KWFinder allows you to conduct keyword research by domain, geographical location, language, and much more. These allow you to zero in on the data you need to power your campaigns. The tool also gives you a clear overview of the SERPs for your chosen keywords.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Like Serpstat, KWFinder has an intuitive dashboard that makes it easy to navigate to the different reports you need.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/mangools/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"320\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-kwfinder-2.png\" alt=\"KWFinder is an SEO keyword analysis tool that comes with a simple and easy to use dashboard.\" class=\"wp-image-64297\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-kwfinder-2.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-kwfinder-2-300x137.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-kwfinder-2-600x274.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Pricing for Mangools&#8217; base plan is $29.90. That&#8217;s a juicy offer for a tool that offers you some of the best features you need to execute effective SEO campaigns.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>5. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/long-tail-pro/\">Long Tail Pro</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>As the name suggests, <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/long-tail-pro/\">Long Tail Pro</a> was designed to help marketers find long-tail keywords to help them rank.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Like the other SEO keyword analysis tools on our list, Long Tail Pro offers tons of data on your keywords and those your competitors are ranking for. This is data such as keyword suggestions with metrics, keyword rankings, and much more.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/long-tail-pro/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"320\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-keyword-analysis-tool-long-tail-pro-2.png\" alt=\"Long Tail Pro is a keyword analysis tool that\'s easy to understand and versatile.\" class=\"wp-image-64515\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-keyword-analysis-tool-long-tail-pro-2.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-keyword-analysis-tool-long-tail-pro-2-300x137.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-keyword-analysis-tool-long-tail-pro-2-600x274.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Designed to help websites rank, Long Tail Pro is a great tool to help you find easy-to-rank-for keywords. A cool feature you&#8217;ll appreciate is that Long Tail Pro color-codes keywords according to search difficulty. The color-coding makes it easier to see at a glance whether your chosen keyword is easy to rank for or not.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As for pricing, Long Tail Pro&#8217;s bottom-tier plan costs $27/month.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>6. <a href=\"https://moz.com/explorer\" rel=\"nofollow\">Moz Keyword Explorer</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://moz.com/explorer\" rel=\"nofollow\">Moz</a> is a name that has almost become synonymous with SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Moz has been in the game for a long time and has established itself as a thought leader. Because of these two facts, they&#8217;ve managed to build an SEO keyword analysis tool that ranks among the best. With Moz&#8217;s <a href=\"https://moz.com/explorer\" rel=\"nofollow\">Keyword Explorer</a>, you can easily conduct:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Competitive keyword analysis</li><li>Sort keywords by predictive metrics (like search volume, difficulty, cost-per-click, e.t.c.)</li><li>Analyze SERPs according to your keyword</li><li>Use various criteria to filter out irrelevant keywords</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://moz.com/explorer\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"439\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-moz-2.png\" alt=\"Moz is an SEO keyword analysis tool that gives a comprehensive overview of your chosen keyword. \" class=\"wp-image-64309\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-moz-2.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-moz-2-300x188.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-moz-2-600x376.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Exporting your keywords into well-formatted CSV files for further analysis is also super-easy. And having been in the business for a long time, Moz has an advanced engine that shows more accurate search metrics than other tools on the market.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Pricing-wise, Moz will set you back $99/month for the base plan.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>7. <a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/ubersuggest/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ubersuggest</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Starting out and looking for a keyword analysis tool that won&#8217;t break the bank?<br>Meet <a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/ubersuggest/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ubersuggest</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ubersuggest offers a lot of important SEO keyword analysis data such as:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Search volume data</li><li>Keyword suggestions</li><li>Keyword difficulty</li><li>Estimated traffic</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/ubersuggest/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"755\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-ubersugest-2.png\" alt=\"Ubersuggest is an SEO keyword analysis tool that\'s becoming popular for its in-depth keyword analysis.\" class=\"wp-image-64311\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-ubersugest-2.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-ubersugest-2-278x300.png 278w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-ubersugest-2-600x647.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Ubersuggest also gives you the average number of backlinks you&#8217;ll need to rank for that keyword. Despite being relatively new on the market, Ubersuggest is fast becoming a force to reckon with in the SEO keyword analysis tool space.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>So, how much will this budget-friendly SEO keyword analysis tool cost you?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ubersuggest&#8217;s lowest-tier plan costs only $12/month and is suited for those running up to three websites.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>8. <a href=\"https://surferseo.com/keyword-surfer-extension/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Keyword Surfer by Surfer SEO</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://surferseo.com/keyword-surfer-extension/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Keyword Surfer</a> is a bit different from the other SEO keyword analysis tools on our list in two ways. First, it&#8217;s a Chrome-based tool. Secondly, it&#8217;s more geared towards on-page content optimization.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Keyword Surfer offers insights into keyword data such as:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Average search volume</li><li>Related keywords</li><li>Questions featured in the top-ranking content</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Surfer&#8217;s Chrome extension is an excellent tool for getting instant insights into your keyword and the content ranking high for it:</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://surferseo.com/keyword-surfer-extension/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"318\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-keyword-finder-2.png\" alt=\"Keyword Finder by Surfer SEO is an excellent SEO keyword analysis for content optimization.\" class=\"wp-image-64321\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-keyword-finder-2.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-keyword-finder-2-300x136.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-keyword-finder-2-600x273.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Compared to the other SEO keyword analysis tools on the list, Keyword Surfer is pretty basic when it comes to in-depth keyword analysis. But it&#8217;s a great tool to have handy if you want to do keyword research on the fly.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The price tag on Keyword Surfer is $34/month.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Which Should You Pick as the Best SEO Keyword Analysis Tool for You?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Choosing the perfect keyword analysis tool can be a daunting task. What with so many different <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-seo-plugins-for-wordpress/\">SEO tools</a> on the market and even more confusing feature-set combinations. To help you make a decision, here are a few recommendations:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>For the best-in-class SEO keyword analysis tool, we recommend Semrush. It has all the features you need to run complete SEO campaigns.</li><li>If you&#8217;re on a shoestring budget, then Ubersuggest is the best SEO keyword analysis tool for you. Despite its limitations in other areas, you&#8217;ll get more than enough data to help you create effective campaigns when it comes to keyword analysis.</li><li>For a keyword analysis tool that helps you optimize your content right on the page, then Keyword Surfer is your go-to keyword analysis tool.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Hopefully, this has helped you narrow down your selection, making it easier to pick the best SEO keyword analysis tool for you.<br>Also, if you&#8217;re looking for a WordPress plugin that will help you <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-hacks-to-grow-your-traffic/\">optimize your website SEO</a>, it doesn&#8217;t get better than All-In-One-SEO. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\">Download AIOSEO here</a>, and let&#8217;s help improve your rankings.</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-seo-keyword-analysis-tool/\">8 Best SEO Keyword Analysis Tools You Need to Know in 2022</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:55:\"https://aioseo.com/best-seo-keyword-analysis-tool/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:75:\"The Best SEO Rank Tracker: 6 Fantastic Tools to Help You Dominate the SERPs\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:106:\"https://aioseo.com/best-seo-rank-tracker/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=best-seo-rank-tracker\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:49:\"https://aioseo.com/best-seo-rank-tracker/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 06 Dec 2021 18:24:56 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"Blog\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:25:\"Best keyword rank tracker\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21:\"Best SEO rank tracker\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"SEO rank tracker\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"https://aioseo.com/?p=62405\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:452:\"<p>What is the best SEO rank tracker on the market?&#160; Knowing where you rank for specific keywords is essential to your overall SEO strategy. After all, ranking top for your keywords ensures that you get the lion&#8217;s share of organic&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-seo-rank-tracker/\">The Best SEO Rank Tracker: 6 Fantastic Tools to Help You Dominate the SERPs</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Kato Nkhoma\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19130:\"<p>What is the best SEO rank tracker on the market?&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Knowing where you <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-find-long-tail-keywords-and-increase-organic-traffic/\">rank for specific keywords</a> is essential to your overall <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-perform-website-seo-analysis-on-wordpress/\">SEO strategy</a>. After all, ranking top for your keywords ensures that you get the lion&#8217;s share of organic search traffic. And that, in turn, means you enjoy more leads and a boost in brand awareness, among many other benefits.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And that&#8217;s why you need the best keyword rank tracker.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>What is an SEO Rank Tracker?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>An SEO rank tracker is an important SEO tool that should be in every serious marketer&#8217;s arsenal. After all, manually checking keyword rankings for every keyword you&#8217;re targeting is next to impossible, because there are usually several keywords, and rank can change regularly.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>That&#8217;s where an SEO rank tracker comes in.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>SEO rank trackers are tools that help you track the performance of your keyword research and general SEO strategies. Simply type in the keywords you want to track, and the tool will do the rest. The rank tracking tool will then monitor your rankings and notify you of any changes to your rankings.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>3 Reasons You Need an SEO Rank Tracker</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>So why should you bother looking for the best SEO rank tracker?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let&#8217;s look at some reasons why you need one, and you&#8217;ll see why.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>1. Monitor and Boost Your Search Rankings</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the most important functions of a rank tracker is — you guessed it — tracking and monitoring your rankings. It&#8217;s essentially helpful for monitoring rank drops. This will help you diagnose the reason behind the rank drop, with some of the most common reasons being:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Technical errors</li><li>Competitors outranking you</li><li>Penalties from search engines</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Whatever the reason, monitoring your rankings is the first port of call if you want to salvage and boost your rankings.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>2. Helps with Competitor Analysis</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Another reason you must invest in the best SEO Rank tracker is because getting one will help you with your competitor analysis.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Rank trackers help you know which <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/check-competitors-keywords/\">keywords your competitors are ranking for.</a> They also give you insight into those they&#8217;re missing out on. This will help you make data-driven decisions concerning your choice of keywords. It will also enable you to create SEO strategies that are more likely to outperform them.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>3. Discover Keyword Opportunities</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Consistent rank tracking is an excellent way of <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-find-related-keywords-in-wordpress/\">spotting keyword trends</a> in your niche. And the more you do it, the easier it becomes to notice keyword opportunities to exploit. This will help you have the edge over your competitors.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With so many benefits, there&#8217;s absolutely no reason why you shouldn&#8217;t use a rank tracker.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>The Best SEO Rank Tracker — 6 You Need to Know&nbsp;</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>With so many rank trackers out there, picking the right one can be quite a daunting task. Here&#8217;s a list of the best SEO rank trackers to help you decide:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>1. <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\">MonsterInsights</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\">MonsterInsights</a> ranks among the best SEO rank trackers for one simple reason — it&#8217;s super easy to use, and it&#8217;s directly in WordPress.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"336\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/best-seo-rank-tracker-monster-insights-1.png\" alt=\"Whe looking for the best SEO rank tracker, MonsterInsights features among the best.\" class=\"wp-image-62507\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/best-seo-rank-tracker-monster-insights-1.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/best-seo-rank-tracker-monster-insights-1-300x144.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/best-seo-rank-tracker-monster-insights-1-600x288.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Created as a Google Analytics plugin for WordPress, MonsterInsights allows you to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/how-to-connect-your-site-with-google-analytics/\">set up Google Analytics in WordPress</a> easily. The beauty of this is that it enables you to view all the data you need right from your WordPress dashboard. Thankfully, this is minus the learning curve that comes with Google Analytics.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With MonsterInsights, you can also view your <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-add-google-search-console-to-your-wordpress-website/\">Google Search Console</a> report to see your website&#8217;s top 50 Google search terms. The dashboard also shows you the average ranking for each. Besides showing you the average position for each keyword, you can also get more detailed SEO-centric data like the number of clicks, impressions, and click-through rate (CTR).&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is all valuable data that will help you optimize your content and boost your rankings. Not only can you use MonsterInsights to boost search rankings, but you can also use it to check pages that are ranking high but have low click-through rates. After all, ranking high doesn&#8217;t do you any good if your pages don&#8217;t convert. When you discover such pages, you can diagnose them and fix the problems causing them not to convert well.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4>MonsterInsights Pricing</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>You can get started with MonsterInsights on the Lite version for free!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>However, you&#8217;ll have to upgrade to the Plus plan to get added features as the Google Search Console reports. And that will set you back $99/year.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>2. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/semrush/\">Semrush</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>One name that constantly rings loud in the world of SEO is <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/semrush/\">Semrush</a>. That&#8217;s because it&#8217;s an excellent all-around SEO tool. It&#8217;s also ranked as one of the best SEO rank trackers on the market.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"306\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/best-seo-rank-tracker-semrush-1.png\" alt=\"Semrush is one of the best SEO rank tracker tools on the market.\" class=\"wp-image-62512\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/best-seo-rank-tracker-semrush-1.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/best-seo-rank-tracker-semrush-1-300x131.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/best-seo-rank-tracker-semrush-1-600x262.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p> Semrush is a powerful SEO tool that allows you to monitor your keyword rankings easily. It also shows you the search terms that have made it to SERP features like featured snippets, knowledge panel, or <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/beginners-guide/how-to-get-google-sitelinks-for-your-wordpress-site/\">Google sitelinks</a>.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With Semrush&#8217;s SERP tracking tools, you can easily understand how you&#8217;re performing in search. At a glance, you can see how many of your keywords are in the top 3, 10, 20, and 100 positions. Not only will the tool show you search rankings, but it also gives you insight into your ranking distribution over time.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides tracking and monitoring your keyword rankings, Semrush also allows you to do the same for your <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-do-an-seo-competitor-analysis/\">competitors&#8217; keywords</a>. This makes it easy to benchmark your SEO performance and know how much work you need to put in if they rank better than you.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4>Semrush Pricing</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Paid Semrush plans will set you back $99.95/month minimum, making it more suited for websites that are already generating decent revenue.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>3. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/ahrefs/\">Ahrefs</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/ahrefs/\">Ahrefs</a> is another tool you should consider investing in if you&#8217;re looking for the best SEO rank tracker.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/ahrefs/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"706\" height=\"269\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/best-seo-rank-tracker-ahrefs.png\" alt=\"Ahrefs ranks as one of the best SEO rank tracker platforms on the market.\" class=\"wp-image-62513\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/best-seo-rank-tracker-ahrefs.png 706w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/best-seo-rank-tracker-ahrefs-300x114.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/best-seo-rank-tracker-ahrefs-704x269.png 704w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/best-seo-rank-tracker-ahrefs-600x229.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 706px) 100vw, 706px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Like Semrush, Ahrefs is an all-in-one marketing platform you can use for all SEO campaigns and more. And when it comes to tracking your rankings on SERPs, it also does an excellent job at that.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tracking your rankings using Ahrefs is easy. All you have to do is import or add the keywords you want to track. Next, add the countries you want to monitor your rankings. Finally, for a comprehensive report, add your competitors&#8217; URLs (up to 10).</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you&#8217;ve uploaded all the relevant information, Ahrefs automatically pulls up ranking data such as:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Search engine rankings</li><li>Visibility percentage</li><li>Average position</li><li>Traffic going to pages ranking for your keywords</li><li>The SERP features you own</li><li>Changes in ranking position</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>While Ahrefs is a powerful SEO tool, the caveat is that it comes with a bit of a learning curve. This is all because it has so many features it can sometimes be overwhelming, particularly for new users.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4>Ahrefs Pricing</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Ahrefs starter plan comes in at $99/month.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>4. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/mangools/\">SERPWatcher by Mangools</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The team at Mangools has been doing a pretty good job with their SEO tools. One of which is <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/mangools/\">SERPWatcher</a>, an SEO ranking tool that&#8217;s fast being noticed as one of the best.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/mangools/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"706\" height=\"239\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/best-seo-rank-tracker-serpwatcher.png\" alt=\"SERPWatcher is one of the best SEO rank tracker platforms on the market.\" class=\"wp-image-62521\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/best-seo-rank-tracker-serpwatcher.png 706w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/best-seo-rank-tracker-serpwatcher-300x102.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/best-seo-rank-tracker-serpwatcher-704x239.png 704w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/best-seo-rank-tracker-serpwatcher-600x203.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 706px) 100vw, 706px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>With a super easy-to-use dashboard, SERPWatcher is one of the best SEO rank trackers for beginner and expert SEOs. Monitoring your rankings is as easy as entering the URL of the domain you want to track (yours or a competitor&#8217;s). You can also import keywords from a spreadsheet or the Mangools KeywordFinder tool.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Once done, you can then click on the &#8220;Start Tracking&#8221; button, and you can:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Set up weekly or monthly reports</li><li>White-label your reports</li><li>Organize your tracking using tags.&nbsp;</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Furthermore, SERPwatcher enables you to view your site&#8217;s performance index, traffic, keyword distribution, position flow, and much more.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4>SERPWatcher Pricing</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>SERPWatch comes with a light $29.90 price tag for the base plan.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>However, the base plan has limited searches, so you&#8217;ll have to be careful with how you use it.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>5. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/se-ranking/\">SE Ranking</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>If you&#8217;re looking for a light-on-the-pockets SEO rank tracker, then <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/se-ranking/\">SE Ranking</a> should be on your radar.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/se-ranking/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"706\" height=\"310\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/best-seo-rank-tracker-se-ranking.png\" alt=\"SE Ranking is one of the best SEO rank tracker tools around.\" class=\"wp-image-62522\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/best-seo-rank-tracker-se-ranking.png 706w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/best-seo-rank-tracker-se-ranking-300x132.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/best-seo-rank-tracker-se-ranking-704x310.png 704w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/best-seo-rank-tracker-se-ranking-600x263.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 706px) 100vw, 706px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>The SE Ranking&#8217;s Keyword Rank Tracker feature allows you to easily monitor your website&#8217;s search terms on major search engines like Google, Bing, Yahoo, Yandex, and YouTube. It also lets you track keywords based on other factors such as geographic locations and devices.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To get started using SE Ranking, enter your site&#8217;s URL, the keywords you want to track, and specify the Search engines and countries you wish to include. You can also add up to 20 competitors&#8217; URLs for tracking.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Because SE Ranking connects to your Google Analytics and Google Search Console, you can expect the results to be accurate.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you have added your website and keywords, you can use SE Ranking&#8217;s dashboard to monitor rankings, view historical data, track competitors, and much more.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4>SE Ranking Pricing</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>SE Rankings prices start from $31/month for tracking 250 keywords and 10 websites.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>6. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/serpstat/\">Serpstat</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>As the name suggests, <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/serpstat/\">Serpstat</a> was designed to help marketers dominate the SERPs by providing them with intelligent and actionable data. That&#8217;s why it makes for one of the best SEO rank trackers on our list.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/serpstat/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"550\" height=\"250\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/best-seo-rank-tracker-serpstat.png\" alt=\"Serpstat is one of the best SEO rank tracker platforms on the market.\" class=\"wp-image-62523\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/best-seo-rank-tracker-serpstat.png 550w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/best-seo-rank-tracker-serpstat-300x136.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>From a simple dashboard, Serpstat allows you to monitor your keyword and <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-best-practices/\">website ranking</a>. Using the Rank Tracker feature, you can create new projects to track your rankings. Doing so involves:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Entering your website details.</li><li>Selecting your search engine options.</li><li>Adding the keywords you want to monitor.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Once done, you can view the position changes of your search terms.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With Serpstat, you can also compare your rankings to those of your competitors, group your keywords, and a whole lot more.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4>Serpstat Pricing</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>The lower-tier plan will cost you $69/month. Being an all-purpose SEO tool, that&#8217;s a steal.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>How to Choose the Best SEO Rank Tracker for Your Needs</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>While this list of the best SEO rank trackers makes picking the right one easier, you still need to whittle the list down to one.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>How do you pick the best keyword rank tracker from all these fantastic rank tracking tools?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are a few factors you can use to help guide your choice:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Budget</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the most important considerations to make when buying anything is whether you have the budget for it. That applies to investing in an SEO rank tracker as well.&nbsp;One thing to note here is that the more features an SEO rank tracker has, the higher the price tag. So, look for a quality rank tracker that doesn&#8217;t come bloated with features you&#8217;ll probably never use. Doing so will ensure you save while getting one of the best tools on the market.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Ease-of-use</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Depending on how tech-savvy you are, ease-of-use is another factor to use when choosing an SEO rank tracker. The easier it is to use, the more time you save.&nbsp;Fortunately, thanks to advancements in technology, many rank trackers are designed with ease-of-use in mind. all you have to do is input the relevant keywords and parameters and the tool will do the rest.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Features</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>While rank tracking is a simple process, you&#8217;ll need to invest in a rank tracker with more features than just rank tracking. This will help you better understand your overall SEO performance. On the same note, look for features you&#8217;ll actually use.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>The Best SEO Rank Tracker Is…&nbsp;</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>What makes for the best SEO rank tracker for one may not be the best one for your specific needs.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>So what&#8217;s the best SEO rank tracker?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We&#8217;ll have to go with MonsterInsights. It strikes the perfect balance between the criteria listed above. MonsterInsights is budget-friendly, provides a wealth of data, and is also easy to use.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>However, if you&#8217;re looking for an all-encompassing SEO tool and have the budget for it, then Semrush fits the bill.&nbsp;Plus, in conjunction with AIOSEO, you can easilywith AIOSEO</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Wrapping Up</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Keeping tabs on your SERP rankings is a critical component of any digital marketing campaign. It helps you effectively grow your online presence, drive more traffic, and improve your conversion rates. That ultimately results in a boost in revenue.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>That&#8217;s why getting the Best SEO rank tracker must be a priority.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And if you need an SEO plugin to bolster your SEO efforts, make sure <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\">to download AIOSEO</a>.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-seo-rank-tracker/\">The Best SEO Rank Tracker: 6 Fantastic Tools to Help You Dominate the SERPs</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:46:\"https://aioseo.com/best-seo-rank-tracker/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:4:\"href\";s:24:\"https://aioseo.com/feed/\";s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:19:\"application/rss+xml\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:44:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/\";a:2:{s:12:\"updatePeriod\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"\n	hourly	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:15:\"updateFrequency\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"\n	1	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}}}}}}s:4:\"type\";i:128;s:7:\"headers\";O:42:\"Requests_Utility_CaseInsensitiveDictionary\":1:{s:7:\"\0*\0data\";a:17:{s:4:\"date\";s:29:\"Tue, 04 Jan 2022 09:29:45 GMT\";s:12:\"content-type\";s:34:\"application/rss+xml; charset=UTF-8\";s:13:\"last-modified\";s:29:\"Thu, 30 Dec 2021 16:27:50 GMT\";s:4:\"etag\";s:34:\"\"18e9af34fc976fced6c8222323b28557\"\";s:15:\"x-frame-options\";s:22:\"SAMEORIGIN, sameorigin\";s:12:\"x-robots-tag\";s:15:\"noindex, follow\";s:4:\"link\";s:55:\"<https://aioseo.com/wp-json/>; rel=\"https://api.w.org/\"\";s:25:\"strict-transport-security\";s:16:\"max-age=15768000\";s:3:\"via\";s:10:\"1.1 google\";s:15:\"cf-cache-status\";s:3:\"HIT\";s:3:\"age\";s:4:\"1817\";s:7:\"expires\";s:29:\"Tue, 04 Jan 2022 13:29:45 GMT\";s:13:\"cache-control\";s:21:\"public, max-age=14400\";s:9:\"expect-ct\";s:87:\"max-age=604800, report-uri=\"https://report-uri.cloudflare.com/cdn-cgi/beacon/expect-ct\"\";s:4:\"vary\";s:15:\"Accept-Encoding\";s:6:\"server\";s:10:\"cloudflare\";s:6:\"cf-ray\";s:20:\"6c8371b978da6b56-AMS\";}}s:5:\"build\";s:14:\"20211223141739\";}', 'no');
