(848, 1, '2021-12-13 15:13:04', '2021-12-13 15:13:04', 'While the interior design profession has emerged since 100 years, the process of interior design has existed for as long as humans have been constructing homes and decorating them based on their needs and materials available to them.Painting interior walls took place for at least 5,000 years, with examples found as far north as the Ness of Brodgar, while Greeks and later Romans added coordinated, decorative mosaics floors, and template bathhouses, shops, civil offices, forts and temples, Ancient Egyptians used interior designing in “soul houses” , they were placed in tombs as receptacles for food offerings And it’s easy to discern details about the interior design of different residences throughout the different Egyptian dynasties, such as changes in ventilation, porticoes, columns, loggias, windows, and doors.', 'History', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'history', '', '', '2021-12-14 16:37:24', '2021-12-14 16:37:24', '', 0, 'http://localhost/hexagon-wordpress/?post_type=about&#038;p=848', 0, 'about', '', 0),
